|       ---------      |    |  -------------------  |   | ------------------------- ---------------- |
|       |dev/vdx|      |    |  |/dev/vhost-vdpa-x|  |   | | vDPA device emulation | | block driver | |
------------+-----------     -----------+------------   -------------+----------------------+---------
