            |                           |                            |                      |
------------+---------------------------+----------------------------+----------------------+---------
|    | block device |           |  vhost device |            | vduse driver |          | TCP/IP |    |
|    -------+--------           --------+--------            -------+--------          -----+----    |
|           |                           |                           |                       |        |
| ----------+----------       ----------+-----------         -------+-------                |        |
| | virtio-blk driver |       |  vhost-vdpa driver |         | vdpa device |                |        |
| ----------+----------       ----------+-----------         -------+-------                |        |
|           |      virtio bus           |                           |                       |        |
|   --------+----+-----------           |                           |                       |        |
|                |                      |                           |                       |        |
|      ----------+----------            |                           |                       |        |
|      | virtio-blk device |            |                           |                       |        |
|      ----------+----------            |                           |                       |        |
|                |                      |                           |                       |        |
|     -----------+-----------           |                           |                       |        |
|     |  virtio-vdpa driver |           |                           |                       |        |
|     -----------+-----------           |                           |                       |        |
|                |                      |                           |    vdpa bus           |        |
